#

Chickpea and Spinach Stuffed Bell Peppers

45 min
$10
250 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy (if using feta)

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

MediterraneanAmerican

Course:

Main CourseVegetarian Dish

Tags:

HealthyQuickEasy

Description

Colorful bell peppers filled with nutritious chickpeas and fresh spinach, perfect for a quick and healthy meal.

Ingredients

  • bell peppers: 4 large
  • canned chickpeas: 1 can (15 oz), drained and rinsed
  • fresh spinach: 2 cups, chopped
  • feta cheese: 1 cup, crumbled (optional)
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • cumin: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
